00:40:42.776 --> 00:40:48.136 A:middle
that you automatically make API
call using the new iOS 8 SDK,

658
00:40:48.136 --> 00:40:52.636 A:middle
and pass that segment
ID onto Workbench.

659
00:40:54.416 --> 00:40:55.736 A:middle
Now when you do that,

